title: Second Date Update: Long Distance Surprise
itunes:title: Second Date Update: Long Distance Surprise
description: What do you do if your perfect match lives 500 miles away? You fly to meet them for your first date! At least, that's what one of our listeners did...He hopped on a plane… And now he's going to hop on the phone with us, because thing didn't go how he expected....
